      propertyPath: journalFullText
      value: 'That dark-green substance is the pollution. It will harm whatever it
        touches. I''m wearing protective boots, so I can walk over it just fine,
        but the slime mold won''t be able to touch it.



        I should be able
        to clean away some of the pollution using my impact rounds. I brought my
        other tools as well in case they come in handy.'
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
